 broader conceptual foundation about environmental changes, external attacks, and internal errors that the source provides. This is worth flagging as a minor omission since an AI would benefit from that fuller context when answering questions about what aspects Robustness actually addresses. I'll include this in my findings.","signature":""}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":2,"cache_creation_input_tokens":12837,"cache_read_input_tokens":18400,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":12837,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":0},"output_tokens":8},"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"e2797727-ff97-41d0-8739-702db6e276d8","uuid":"f9840d94-21fa-488a-b91d-033b5b7dc67b"}
